title: #38 Rener Gracie, Oathkeepers and Hilarious Trump Quotes!
description: This week, Rener Gracie stops by to talk about one of his pupils who thwarted the France terrorist attack! We're also joined by founder/head of the Oathkeepers who have raised some eyebrows in Ferguson. Also, Stalker Jim and Sweet Avery call in!
